Package ou

Class Summary
OUAnimatedObject OUAnimatedObject forms the base class of all objects used in M250 which have a graphical representation in a microworld.
OUColour Extends java.awt.Color to include an improved toString() method and static colours BROWN and PURPLE.
OUDialog OUDialog provides static methods to display dialog boxes either to display results or request information.
OUFileChooser OUFileChoose provides static methods to all the user to select a file for input or output.
